---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Learn more about Nora and Baked by Noz custom sugar cookies."
	pubDate={new Date('June 01 2025')}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<p>
		Hi, I'm Nora aka Noz! I am the baker, decorator, and creative mind behind <strong>Baked by Noz</strong>.
	</p>

	<p>
		What started as a special treat for my nephew's birthday in June of 2025 has grown into a business that allows me to be a part of life's most special celebrations.
	</p>

	<h2>Crafted with Care</h2>
	<p>
		Every cookie is baked from scratch using quality ingredients and hand-decorated with care and attention to detail. I love turning ideas into edible works of art, whether it's a child's favourite character, elegant wedding favours, personalised gifts, or branded corporate cookies.
	</p>

	<h2>More Than Just Cookies</h2>
	<p>
		For me, it's about more than just making cookies it's about creating something that brings people together, starts conversations, and becomes part of lasting memories. Seeing the excitement on my customers' faces when they receive their order is one of the most rewarding parts of what I do.
	</p>

	<h2>How to Order</h2>
	<p>
		Ready to order custom cookies for your upcoming event?
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Get in touch:</strong> Email me at bakedbynoz@gmail.com or send me a DM on <a href="https://www.instagram.com/bakedbynoz" target="_blank">Instagram (@bakedbynoz)</a>.</li>
		<li><strong>Include event details:</strong> Share your event date, theme or inspiration photos, and estimated cookie count.</li>
		<li><strong>Custom quote:</strong> I'll review availability and provide a quote tailored to your request!</li>
	</ul>

	<br />

	<p>
		Thank you for supporting my small business. I am so grateful to be trusted with your special moments and I can't wait to create something delicious just for you!
	</p>

	<p>
		<em>With love,<br />Nora x</em>
	</p>
</Layout>
